											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Shadowheart steps towards the waypoint to exit the Shadowfell, then freezes, sensing something. She glances around - there is nobody else in sight. Suddenly her incurable wound flares up and she collapses with a cry of pain. Shar's disembodied voice booms down." />
